Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: New York's ethnic mix
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040btb3
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 10 Sep 1978
The delicate political balancing act between the ethnic minorities which make up New York. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less